113 section for the entire period of time the voter remains on the
114 voter registration list.
115 (g) The Secretary of State shall adopt rules to
116 implement this section.
117 Section 2. Sections 17-3-52, 17-13-1, 17-13-7, and
118 17-13-47, Code of Alabama 1975, are amended to read as
